{"word":"G253 - ἀλυπότερος - alypóteros - al-oo-pot'-er-os - Less sorrowful","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀλυπότερος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">alypóteros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">al-oo-pot'-er-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Less sorrowful</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"துக்கங்குறைந்த - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"free from pain or grief"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Comparative of a compound of <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G3077 - λύπη - lýpē - loo'-pay/3077\">G3077</a>; <i>more without grief:</i> - less sorrowful.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G253/253\">G253</a>, <a href=\"#/G3076/3076\">G3076</a>, <a href=\"#/G3077/3077\">G3077</a>, <a href=\"#/G4036/4036\">G4036</a>, <a href=\"#/G4818/4818\">G4818</a>"}]}